  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE NEW SECTION 61-3-65, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE AIRPORT AUTHORITIES TO TAKE POSSESSION OF, OBTAIN TITLE TO, AND DISPOSE OF ABANDONED MOTOR VEHICLES LEFT UPON AIRPORT PROPERTY; TO SET FORTH NOTICE REQUIREMENTS; TO AUTHORIZE SALE, DISPOSAL, OR RETENTION FOR AIRPORT USE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
